pmmd.notes: The most parsimonious tree of the analysis of the ITS region. Asterisks indicate posterior probabilities of 1.00. Only PB > 50 and PP > 95 are shown. Abbreviations: PB = percentage bootstrap support, PP = posterior probability, Digitalis o. = Digitalis obscura, Digitalis p. = Digitalis purpurea, Globularia r. = Globularia repens, Globularia s. = Globularia salicina
